childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$1Dodongo's Cavern...^$2Spirit Temple...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Forest Temple...^$3Link's Pocket...^$4Water Temple...^$5Shadow Temple...^$6Fire Temple...^$7Deku Tree...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: Today, let's begin down&'The Hero is Defeated' timeline.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rSpirit Temple%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rLake Hylia%w!

dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rDodongo's Cavern%w. I will let&you have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Damp√©
